                        OFIS FACTS
                    </div>
                    <div class='module_content'>
                        <div class='ofis_fact'><p>OFIS - The Ontario Federation of Independent Schools - is a legally incorporated, duly constituted service association for independent schools, established in 1974....</p></div><div class='ofis_fact'><p>"Parents have a prior right to FREELY choose the kind of education that shall be given to their child" – 1948 UN Universal Declaration of Human Rights, Article 26, Section 3...</p></div>                    </div>

